Generisk dokument som inneholder sammendrag av helseinformasjon om et individ.
Documento genérico que contiene un resumen de la información de salud sobre un individuo.

en.purpose: For the recording of organisation details aligned with corresponding FHIR resource.
en.use:
Use to record organisation details aligned with the corresponding FHIR resources.

The slots for telecoms, address and contact should be filled with the appropriate FHIR resource-aligned clusters.

This cluster archetype is intended to be used inside FHIR resource aligned archetypes such as CLUSTER.fhir_contact.v0 and CLUSTER.fhir_practitioner.v0.

en.purpose: For the recording of identifier details aligned with corresponding FHIR resource or data types.
en.use:
Use to record identifier details aligned with the corresponding FHIR resources or data types.

This cluster archetype is intended to be used inside the Identifier slot in any FHIR resource-aligned archetypes. These may be clusters themselves or entry archetypes.
